videos.description: Players and coaches from both the Lakers and the Spurs gather at center court to link arms during the singing of the national anthem before the start of their contest.

videos.headline: Lakers, Spurs link arms for anthem before game

videos.description: Talen Horton-Tucker drives into the lane and throws a slick look-away pass to Anthony Davis to set him up for an emphatic two-handed dunk.

videos.headline: Horton-Tucker drops sweet dime to AD for the jam
